sentences.english: Teacher is a key factor in actualizing education for quality.
sentences.chinese: 教师是实施素质教育的关键因素。

sentences.english: It is an inevitable choice to develop the strategy of famous brand for an enterprise in the keen market competitions.
sentences.chinese: 实施名牌战略是企业在激烈的市场竞争中的必然选择。

sentences.english: Just show me one county where Dr. Sun's principles have been put in practice.
sentences.chinese: 你给我指出哪一个县实施了孙中山先生的三民主义？

sentences.english: The raid was conducted with U. S. military personnel assaulting on two helicopters.
sentences.chinese: 实施袭击的是两驾直升机上的美国军方人员。

sentences.english: Implementing customer scenarios to include the flow of defect submissions expands integration coverage.
sentences.chinese: 包含缺陷交付流程的实施客户场景扩展了集成的范围。

sentences.english: China is implementing a family planning policy. So I'm the only child in my family.
sentences.chinese: 中国正在实施计划生育政策，所以我是家中的独生子。

sentences.english: In the implementation of this cross-century strategy, ethnic issues merit special attention.
sentences.chinese: 民族问题在这项跨世纪战略的实施中具有特殊的地位。

sentences.english: This is a superb concept. It should certainly be done.
sentences.chinese: 这是一种极好的概念，当然应该实施。

sentences.english: How do these issues influence the implementation and improvement of BASIX?
sentences.chinese: 这些问题是怎样影响BASIX的实施和改善的？

sentences.english: They are currently in the process of piloting two programs aimed at getting families outdoors.
sentences.chinese: 他们最近还在实施另两个旨在让家庭走向户外的项目。

sentences.english: They (China) are mistakenly trying to impose a flawed Monroe Doctrine in their backyard.
sentences.chinese: 中国错误的想在自己的后院实施有缺陷的门罗主义。

sentences.english: Did their parents check up on their whereabouts and set curfews?
sentences.chinese: 他们的父母会调查他们的行踪并实施宵禁吗？

sentences.english: Thus, embodiments of a virtual local memory for a graphics processor are disclosed.
sentences.chinese: 这样，公开了图形处理器的虚拟本地存储器的实施例。

sentences.english: After hacker attack website is procurable, carry out " hang a horse " .
sentences.chinese: 当黑客攻击网站得手后，便实施“挂马”。

sentences.english: Since 2003, the Tourism-based Country Strategy has been established and implemented in Japan.
sentences.chinese: 自2003年以来，日本确立并实施了观光立国战略。

sentences.english: Cross-sectoral international collaboration key to implementing IHR.
sentences.chinese: 跨部门的国际合作是实施《国际卫生条例》的关键。
